'''Randy Martinez''' is an artist. He drew the program cover for both [[Celebration IV]] and [[Celebration Europe (2007)|Celebration Europe]]. He did the covers for all books in the ''[[Star Wars: Rebel Force]]'' series and for the book ''[[Darth Vader: Sith Lord]]''. He also worked on the art of several ''Star Wars'' pinball machine games, including one for ''[[Star Wars: The Mandalorian]]''.<ref name="Pinball">{{SW|url=news/the-mandalorian-stern-pinball|text=The Mandalorian's Next Mission? Pinball.}}</ref>

